text:
So In 2017 I was on unemployment in NY. I had a Key2Benefits debit card.

This card expired in 2019.

I just filed a claim a. few days ago. My payment history says payment released today April 21st 2020

Seeing as how my card expired in 2019

Will they be sending me a new debit card?

Should I assume the card is already on it's way to me seeing as how the payment was released already?

edit: IM not sure if I need to request one with Key Bank or if they will just send me one. The wait is 4 hours to speak to a representative.

THANKS for any help
title: NYS Unemployment. will I be receiving a new card?
